com.serotonin.bacnet4j.event

Class DeviceEventHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.serotonin.bacnet4j.event.DeviceEventHandler

  • public class DeviceEventHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to handle various events that occur on the local device. This class accepts 0 to many listeners, and dispatches notifications synchronously.
    Author:
    Matthew Lohbihler
